        descriptionFull: 'It is an easy to use résumé constructor. It walks you through all the steps and gives a complete CV at the end. You can save it as a PDF and use to apply for your dream job.',
        slogan: 'Creating résumés made as easy as never before.',
        stack: ['React', 'TailwindCSS', 'DaisyUI']
    },
    {
        name: 'Resumatiq',
        descriptionShort: 'An easy to use resume creator',
